      <title>英国民调结果惨淡，暴露苏纳克面临的挑战有多大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/scale-of-sunak-s-challenge-laid-bare-by-disastrous-uk-polling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离英国大选不到三周，首相里希·苏纳克（Rishi Sunak）上周末遭遇了灾难性的民意调查，这表明他在 7 月 4 日投票前扭转保守党命运的可能性很小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/scale-of-sunak-s-challenge-laid-bare-by-disastrous-uk-polling</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国、瑞士金融公司位居欧洲董事会政治关联排行榜榜首</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/french-swiss-banks-more-likely-to-have-politicians-on-boards-than-europe-peers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安永的一项研究显示，法国和瑞士的金融公司聘请前政治家担任董事会成员的可能性比其欧洲同行更高，凸显了两国政策制定与金融世界之间的紧密联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/french-swiss-banks-more-likely-to-have-politicians-on-boards-than-europe-peers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
