      <title>美国东北部遭遇本季首波热浪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/northeastern-us-to-swelter-in-the-first-heat-wave-of-the-season</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本季第一股强烈热浪从五大湖延伸至大西洋，将增加电力需求、减缓交通网络，同时威胁健康风险。]]></description>
